item.title: Side Navigation
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
AZUL Includes Sidebar Menu Option

  Azul includes a sidebar option with second level. Nowyou can add more content to your site. Its very easy to set up with custom menu and widget option. Check out all other great features of Azul.

item.title: Advanced Admin Panel
item.dc:creator: admin

item.title: Blog Options
item.dc:creator: admin

item.title: Boxed and Wide Version
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Boxed and wide version

  Azul comes in a boxed or a wide layout, and can easily be switched in the admin panel. The layout style will be applied throughout the entire site. When you have the boxed version activated, you can choose to have the background be a custom image, a pattern or a solid color! Azul comes with 9 pre-defined patterns to choose from.

item.title: Custom Backgrounds
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Custom backgrounds

  You can upload custom images to the background of the boxed version, or you can use one of our 9 predefined patterns or use a solid color!

item.title: Custom Widgets
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Custom widgets

  Were trying to make your job easier, so weve included lots of widgets that you can easily drag and drop to activate and customize. Text area, Twitter, Flickr, Social Links, Categories, Search Field and more.

item.title: Font Options
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Font options

  Azul includes over 500+ Google Fonts, Standard Fonts and you can upload custom fonts. Happy "Fonting"

item.title: Great Support
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Great support

  What to say, try us!

item.title: One Click Demo Content
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
One Click Demo Content

  Set up demo content simply with one click, or import it.

item.title: 23 PSD files
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
23 PSD Files

  We included 23 PSD files in value of 10$ so you can really customise your theme all the way.

item.title: Portfolio options
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Portfolio Options

Choose between 1,2,3 or 4 column view, filter it and set the limit, easy and fast trough our admin panel.

item.title: Translation Ready
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Translation Ready

  Azul is translation ready with the included .mo and .po language files.

item.title: Unlimited Colors
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Unlimited Colors

  Azul comes with 10 pre made color schemes, but you can customise it for your needs. Control the colour of your page with Azul.

item.title: Unlimited Sidebars
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Unlimited Sidebars

  Azul gives you an option to create unlimited number of your own custom sidebars, which you then insert with widgets.
